3. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses the application of the proposed protocol to satellite communication channels, which is a topic related to networking and internet architecture. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper proposes a protocol that involves the transmission of information over a noisy channel, which is a topic related to systems and control. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper does not directly deal with multimedia, but it does involve the transmission of information over channels, which is a topic related to multimedia.
